name: Dipped Dress
description:
Hand Dyed this strapless dress features a customized ombre' effect which is created by hand by me. Shown here in green but you there are a choice of other colours too! 

Every dress is one of a kind, and I am able to take the dye higher or lower depending on the effect you are after. The dress can be made shorter if you like. But Midi length (featured) is as long as you can go! :) 

Ribbon Belt Not Included.

name: Water lights Sequin Maxi Skirt
description:
Sequins & Floral, what's not to like? This stunning sequin has the most glorious floral patten that makes it a true, one of a kind statement piece! 

If you don't want the side spilt, not an issue, just add the customization option when you check out!

name: Astrid Baby Skirt
description:
One of my first pieces and still an all time favourite. This skirt works with any kind of top, basic tanks, capped or puff sleeve tees or even floral tops! 

A beautiful silky fabric this skirt is available in a lavender, pale pink (pictured),white, blue & a lush raspberry pink! What colour are you?

name: Customization
description:
Want your skirt, pants or jumpsuit to fit just right? Need more length? Want to shorten the hem? Need a halter neck? No problem! Just add this to your cart and message me with your order number and let me know what you need! 

Photo Info: This was a custom made version of the Tiger Lilly Skirt that I made for From The Rez To The City for her to wear during Full Figured Fashion Week, 2013 in New York City! 

Photo Credit: From The Rez To The City, http://fromthereztothecity.blogspot.com.au/

name: Arabian Princess Sequin Harem Pants
description:
The are a special, made to measure order. From standing out on a Friday night to sparkling on that special occasion, these are a stand out piece every closet needs! 

Available for Lay By // Lay Away: Please feel free to get in touch via the contact page!
